# Minimal build context: only the package + the baked LG A/C IR asset.
# Everything else (secrets, runtime state, captures, tests, docs, git) is kept
# out of the context entirely, so it can never leak into an image layer.
*
!hestia/
!hestia/**
!tools/
!tools/klima.ir
!requirements.txt
!ui/
!ui/**
ui/node_modules/
ui/node_modules/**
ui/dist/
ui/dist/**
